text: Yannick de Wit (born 26 August 1986) is a Dutch footballer who plays as a midfielder for Tweede Klasse club Blauw-Wit Beursbengels. ==Career== Born in Zaanstad, De Wit is a product of the Ajax youth system. He also played for FC Volendam, Go Ahead Eagles and FC Emmen. After leaving the latter, De Wit started playing amateur football for ASV De Dijk and later moved to HBOK.
